About Sebastian
Your Best Vacation Ever Starts Here
Visit the Sebastian Chamber of Commerce
View the hotspots in Sebastian, FL
Find Us: Directions and Map of our Property
The Sebastian Inlet is
within minutes
from our docks, allows access to the Atlantic Ocean from the Indian River for deep sea fishing and other sport.
Sebastian offers a variety of river view restaurants, live music venues, galleries, parks, marina, public boat ramps, water sports, and shopping. All are within walking distance or a short bike ride away from the resort.
Medical facilities, banks, churches, golf, and shopping are all within minutes of the resort. Vero Beach and Melbourne are within a half-hour drive and offer additional activities including theater, concerts, museums, art galleries, and beautiful ocean beaches.
Visit the
Sebastian Chamber of Commerce
web site to see all this special area has to offer.
